# END OF REDIRECT MAP
# =============================================================================
# Summary:
#   - 18 BAM course redirects (explicit) + ~40 city pattern redirects
#   - 13 BAS P/U course redirects (explicit) + ~120 city pattern redirects
#   - 6 SAM/Skyddsombud redirects
#   - 7 Ledarskap redirects
#   - 6 Webbutbildningar redirects + catch-all patterns
#   - 4 Fysiska utbildningar redirects + catch-all patterns
#   - 5 Engelska utbildningar redirects + catch-all
#   - 2 Krisutbildningar redirects + catch-all
#   - 4 Lararledda webbutbildningar redirects + catch-all
#   - 20 Vara tjanster/Kunskapsbank redirects + catch-all patterns
#   - 4 Om Oss sub-page redirects
#   - 4 Nyheter/Kursmaterial/Personal redirects
#   - 6 Special/company-specific redirects
#   - 2 Taxonomy/category redirects + catch-all
#   - 100+ Kunskapsbanken article pattern redirects (regex)
